#### How to run
```
$ pip install pluto
```

```
# create custom bar_plot
bar_plot = Barplot()
# configuring custom bar_plot
bar_plot.shape(dim=(10, 5))
    .create('x_col', 'y_col', table, hue='z_col', c=None)
    .grid()
    .spine()
    .tick(left=True, labelleft=True, bottom=True, labelbottom=True)
    .label('x axis', 'y axis', 'title')
    .render()

```
